:: Intro {"position":"700,0","size":"100,100"}
<<nobr>>
The Ghost Hunter<br>
<br>
<b>What’s your extra sensitive spot?</b><br>
<em>The chosen one will occur more frequently during the ghost hunt than the other body parts, bringing more lust.</em><br>
<label><<radiobutton "$sensualBodyPart.brain" 3 autocheck>> Mind</label><br>
<label><<radiobutton "$sensualBodyPart.tits" 3 autocheck>> Boobs</label><br>
<label><<radiobutton "$sensualBodyPart.ass" 3 autocheck>> Ass</label><br>
<label><<radiobutton "$sensualBodyPart.mouth" 3 autocheck>> Tongue</label><br>
<label><<radiobutton "$sensualBodyPart.pussy" 3 autocheck>> Pussy</label><br>
<label><<radiobutton "$sensualBodyPart.anal" 3 autocheck>> Anus</label><br>
Enter your name here: <<textbox "$mc.name" "Mary" "Intro1">>and press "Enter".
<br>
Or just click @@.enterbtn;<<link "here" "Intro1">><<set $mc.name to "Mary">><</link>>@@ 

<br>
<br>
<br>
@@.mc-thoughts;This game is similar to games like Phasmophobia, Demonologist, etc., so if you've played such games, there shouldn't be any difficulties. Nevertheless, here's a brief guide to the game:@@
<br>
@@.enterbtn;[[guide]]@@ 
<</nobr>>




:: Intro1 {"position":"700,100","size":"100,100"}
<div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
  <div style="flex: 1;">
&emsp;&emsp;	You are $mc.name, a brave young woman who has devoted much of her free time to studying esoterics, mysticism, and the unexplainable. Somehow, it drew you more than anything else, perhaps because in your world, incredible creatures, from ghosts to demons, have started appearing. This has been going on for quite some time. 
&emsp;&emsp;The world has changed, and society has changed with it. People have grown accustomed to such anomalies, but there are cases when certain measures have to be taken. This led to the emergence of new professions: ghost hunters, witches, exorcists, and so on.</div>
 <div style="flex: 1; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;">
<img src="assets/img/mc.jpg" width="80%"><br>  </div>
</div>
&emsp;&emsp;@@.mc-speech; Such professions are quite dangerous, but the risk is worth it: they pay quite well@@ - you think.
&emsp;&emsp;And so, you have dedicated yourself to this. You are a ghost hunter. Of course, you lack experience; you have some knowledge and minimal inexpensive equipment, but you have a strong desire to start contributing to society and, well, to earn some money.
&emsp;&emsp;You live alone in a small town. However, even here, there is work for you. They say there's a witch nearby who can help you with your job. She provides contracts for ghosts. Most likely, she is a middleman or something similar.
&emsp;&emsp;@@.mc-speech; I think it's best to head to the witch first. She should advise me on what to do.@@

@@.mc-action; Visit the witch, she should provide details.@@

@@.enterbtn;[[Start|CityMap]] @@ 



:: Ironclad Prison {"position":"2700,525","size":"100,100"}
<<nobr>>
<img src="assets/room/ironclad/ironclad.webp" width="90%"><br>
@@.location; Prison "Ironclad"@@<br>
@@.mc-thoughts; Ironclad Prison, once a symbol of justice, now stands abandoned, its long and storied past cloaked in shadows. Whispers speak of restless spirits wandering its halls—a chilling reminder of the darkness it once held.@@<br>
<br>


<<if $wardenClothesStage eq 2>>
@@.movebtn;[[Go inside|IroncladHallway][$ghostHuntingMode to 2]]@@<br>
<<else>>
@@.movebtn; <<linkreplace "Go inside">>
<<set $wardenClothesStage to 0>>
<<set $mc.energy to 0>>
@@.mc-thoughts; You walk through the prison, exploring every room. But nothing happens.@@<br>
@@.mc-speech; Something's not right. This is definitely the place, but there are no ghosts... I guess I should ask the witch. @@<br><br>
@@.backbtn; [[Return home|Home][$hours += 6; $isIronclad to 0]] @@<br>
<</linkreplace>>@@
<</if>>
<br>
<br>
<<if $ghostHuntingMode eq 2>><span class="movebtn">[[End the hunt|HuntOverManual][$ghostHuntingMode to 3]]</span><<else>><</if>>
<</nobr>>



:: IroncladBlockA [IroncladBlockA hauntedhouse] {"position":"2600,300","size":"100,100"}
<<nobr>>
<div class="room">
	<div class="room-wrapper">
		<div class="content">
          	<div id="actionironcladBlockA" class="action">
				
          	</div>
        </div>
        
		<div class="footer">
        	<div class="footertools">
         	<div class="footer-card">
            	<div class="cardimg">
                	<img src="assets/img/emf.png" class="icon" id="ironcladBlockAPicEMF">
                </div>
                <div class="cardlink">
                	<<include "searchEMFBlockAIronclad">>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-card">
            	<div class="cardimg">
                	<img src="assets/img/glass.png" class="icon" id="actionironcladBlockAPicPlasm">                
                </div>
                <div class="cardlink">
                	<<include "searchPlasmBlockAIronclad">>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-card">
            	<div class="cardimg">
                	<img src="assets/img/gwb.png" class="icon" id="actionironcladBlockAPicGWB">                
                </div>
                <div class="cardlink">
                	<<include "searchGwbBlockAIronclad">>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-card">
            	<div class="cardimg">
                	<img src="assets/img/spiritbox.png" class="icon" id="actionironcladBlockAPicSB">                
                </div>
                <div class="cardlink">
                	<<include "searchSbBlockAIronclad">>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-card">
            	<div class="cardimg">
                	<img src="assets/img/thermometr.png" class="icon" id="actionironcladBlockAPicThermometr">                
                </div>
                <div class="cardlink">
                	<<include "searchThermometrBlockAIronclad">>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-card">
            	<div class="cardimg">
                	<img src="assets/img/uvl.png" class="icon" id="actionironcladBlockAPicUVL">                
                </div>
                <div class="cardlink">
                	<<include "searchUvlBlockAIronclad">>
                </div>
            </div>
              <<if $showComp eq 1>>
            <div class="footer-card">
            	<div class="cardimg">
					<<compLinks>>              
                </div>
            </div>
            <<elseif $showComp eq 2>>
            <div class="footer-card">
            	<div class="cardimg">
                <a data-passage="failedComp">
                	<img src="assets/img/questionMark.png" class="companion-image"> </a>     
                </div>
            </div>
            <<elseif $showComp eq 3>>
            <div class="footer-card">
            	<div class="cardimg">
<<compLinksSuccess>>
                </div>
            </div>
            <</if>>
            <div class="footer-card footer-light">
            	<span class="cursedHuntLinkDisable"><<link [img[assets/img/lighton.png][IroncladBlockA]]>><<set $BlockA.background to 1>><</link>>
             <<link [img[assets/img/lightoff.png][IroncladBlockA]]>><<set $BlockA.background to 2>><</link>>
			<<if $mc.lust gte 80 and $weakenTheGhostQuest and $isWeakenGhost neq 1>> 
<<link [img[assets/img/hearth.png][minigame]]>>
<<set $minigameVideo to "start">>
<<set $ghostOrgasmMeter to 0>>
<<set $mcOrgasmMeter to 0>><</link>>
<</if>></span>
            </div>
         </div>
         <div class="footeraction">
			@@.adaptiveLink;<<link "CellA" "IroncladBlockACellA">>
<<includeTimeEventHunt>><<set $stepCount += 1>><</link>>@@   
			@@.adaptiveLink;<<link "CellB" "IroncladBlockACellB">>
<<includeTimeEventHunt>><<set $stepCount += 1>><</link>>@@  
			@@.adaptiveLink;<<link "CellC" "IroncladBlockACellC">>
<<includeTimeEventHunt>><<set $stepCount += 1>><</link>>@@  
			@@.adaptiveLink;<<link "Entrance" "IroncladHallway">>
<<includeTimeEventHunt>><<set $stepCount += 1>><</link>>@@  
		 </div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<</nobr>>


