:: LFCI {"position":"2200,1150","size":"100,100"}
<<nobr>>
@@.mc-thoughts; You try to find something, but it seems like nothing is there. Suddenly, you feel an unusual warmth emanating from one of the objects. As you get closer and touch it, the warmth intensifies, spreading throughout your body like an internal heat. Only when you bring the object closer to yourself do you realize that @@@@.mc-speech;<<linkappend "it is a ">><br>
<<set _check to random(1,4)>>
<<if _check eq 1>>@@.mc-speech; Dildo???@@<br><img src="assets/cursedItems/dildo.png" width="30%">
<<set $isCIDildo to 1>><</if>>
<<if _check eq 2>>@@.mc-speech; Buttplug???@@<br><img src="assets/cursedItems/buttplug.png" width="30%">
<<set $isCIButtplug to 1>><</if>>
<<if _check eq 3>>@@.mc-speech; Anal beads???@@<br><img src="assets/cursedItems/beads.png" width="30%">
<<set $isCIBeads to 1>><</if>>
<<if _check eq 4>>@@.mc-speech; Huge dildo???@@<br><img src="assets/cursedItems/monsterdildo.png" width="30%">
<<set $isCIHDildo to 1>><</if>>
<br>
Well, the cursed and mysterious item turns out to be... this. I’m not  surprised. Well, I’ll need to take it to the witch. <br>
Damn, as soon as I picked up this item, I immediately felt more... aroused.<br>
+30 <img src="assets/img/hearth.png" style="position: relative; top: 0.375em; width:3%;"><br><<include "add30lust">>
<<set $gotCursedItem to 1>>
[[Continue investigating the house|previous()]] Or perhaps... <<linkreplace "Use it">>
<<include "UseCursedItem">>
<</linkreplace>><br> <</linkappend>>@@ 
<<done>>
<<addclass ".linkselector" "disabled-link">>
<</done>>
<</nobr>>


:: Library {"position":"2500,1700","size":"100,100"}
<<nobr>>
<img src="assets/img/library.jpg" width="100%">
<br>
@@.location; Library@@<br>
@@.mc-thoughts; This library boasts a diverse collection of books, including both modern publications and rare antique editions. Although most people prefer to search for information online, a few still visit, perhaps in search of more unusual and unique insights.@@<br>
<br>
<<if $hours lte 7 or $hours gte 22>>
<<else>>
