@@.mc-speech;And how do I do that?@@<br>
@@.notmc-speech;Use your body to arouse him. Show who's in charge in this haunted house.@@<br>
@@.mc-speech;I think I get what you mean... I'm not sure I can do it...@@<br>
@@.notmc-speech;I'll pay you extra for this task.@@<br>
@@.mc-speech;Okay, I'll think about it.@@<br><br>
@@.mc-action; Now you can perform the witch's additional task: weaken the ghost.@@<br>
<<set $weakenTheGhostQuest to 1>>
