:: cursedHuntStart [nobr noreturn] {"position":"2700,1100","size":"100,100"}
<video autoplay muted class="displayCentredImgs">
<source src="assets/hunting/huntEnd.mp4" type="video/mp4">
</video>
@@.mc-thoughts;You couldn’t find a hiding spot, and before you even realize what’s happening, you’re@@<<linkappend "@@.usebtn; grabbed by him.@@">>
